Predictive Performance is a Measure
Accuracy is a Metric
Recall is a Metric
ROC AUC Score is a Metric
Accuracy contributes to Predictive Performance
Recall contributes to Predictive Performance
ROC AUC Score contributes to Predictive Performance

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Sklearn Metric interface — plain function: (y_true, y_pred, **kw) -> number
# Individual metrics may add operator-specific kwargs (e.g. average="weighted").
# Interface-level I/O applies to all ``Sklearn Metric`` operators unless the
# operator overrides specific ports (e.g. roc_auc_score uses y_score).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sklearn Metric is an Interface
Sklearn Metric has input y_true; is of type any; has position y_true
Sklearn Metric has input y_pred; is of type any; has position y_pred
Sklearn Metric has output score; is of type float; has position score

# Classification metrics
F1 Score is a Metric
F1 Score contributes to Predictive Performance
Precision is a Metric
Precision contributes to Predictive Performance

sklearn.metrics.accuracy_score is an Operator
sklearn.metrics.accuracy_score is a Sklearn Metric
sklearn.metrics.accuracy_score implements Accuracy
sklearn.metrics.accuracy_score evaluates Classification

sklearn.metrics.f1_score is an Operator
sklearn.metrics.f1_score is a Sklearn Metric
sklearn.metrics.f1_score implements F1 Score
sklearn.metrics.f1_score evaluates Classification

sklearn.metrics.precision_score is an Operator
sklearn.metrics.precision_score is a Sklearn Metric
sklearn.metrics.precision_score implements Precision
sklearn.metrics.precision_score evaluates Classification

sklearn.metrics.recall_score is an Operator
sklearn.metrics.recall_score is a Sklearn Metric
sklearn.metrics.recall_score implements Recall
sklearn.metrics.recall_score evaluates Classification

# Regression metrics
R-squared is a Metric
R-squared contributes to Predictive Performance
RMSE is a Metric
RMSE contributes to Predictive Performance
MAE is a Metric
MAE contributes to Predictive Performance

sklearn.metrics.r2_score is an Operator
sklearn.metrics.r2_score is a Sklearn Metric
sklearn.metrics.r2_score implements R-squared
sklearn.metrics.r2_score evaluates Regression

sklearn.metrics.mean_squared_error is an Operator
sklearn.metrics.mean_squared_error is a Sklearn Metric
sklearn.metrics.mean_squared_error implements RMSE
sklearn.metrics.mean_squared_error evaluates Regression

sklearn.metrics.mean_absolute_error is an Operator
sklearn.metrics.mean_absolute_error is a Sklearn Metric
sklearn.metrics.mean_absolute_error implements MAE
sklearn.metrics.mean_absolute_error evaluates Regression

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Data-quality metrics and default thresholds
# These defaults are used for DQ checks unless the user supplies an override.
