SyntacticDataAccuracy is a Metric
SyntacticDataAccuracy has decision function constant_threshold
SyntacticDataAccuracy has threshold 0.95
SemanticDataAccuracy is a Metric
SemanticDataAccuracy has decision function constant_threshold
SemanticDataAccuracy has threshold 0.95
